00:07:48.100 --> 00:07:49.930
Can you take us right now?

00:07:49.971 --> 00:07:51.319
And we're ready to pay double the price.

00:07:51.860 --> 00:07:53.336
He says, no, no, I can't, I'm booked up until 7 p.m.

00:07:54.819 --> 00:07:56.778
I say, but we're ready to pay double, even at 7 p.m.

00:07:57.281 --> 00:08:00.839
No, no, even if you pay three or four times, I won't take you.

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:04.514
Wow, what a mindset!

00:08:04.533 --> 00:08:05.317
Can you imagine that mindset?

00:08:05.843 --> 00:08:06.812
