00:09:15.942 --> 00:09:16.879
It's true for your health.

00:09:17.464 --> 00:09:18.357
It's true for your work.

00:09:18.780 --> 00:09:20.039
It's true for your business partners.

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:21.019
It's true for everything.

00:09:21.461 --> 00:09:24.019
You shouldn't be afraid to go for it.

00:09:24.221 --> 00:09:26.500
There are still 7 billion people on this planet.

00:09:26.783 --> 00:09:27.519
Maybe even more, I don't even know anymore.

00:09:27.820 --> 00:09:29.080
