00:09:29.301 --> 00:09:33.220
But you'll find the right people who will invest in your companies,

00:09:33.703 --> 00:09:35.019
who will bring you great deals,

00:09:35.400 --> 00:09:37.639
who will help you get to the next level,

00:09:37.881 --> 00:09:39.177
who will make up for your weaknesses.

00:09:39.643 --> 00:09:41.035
Who here has no flaws?

00:09:44.683 --> 00:09:45.878
