00:09:48.299 --> 00:09:48.806
But also 150 strengths.

00:09:51.182 --> 00:09:54.000
So we all have flaws, we all have weaknesses, we all have strengths.

00:09:55.080 --> 00:09:56.860
And there are two types of schools.

00:09:57.303 --> 00:09:58.179
I'm still in the intro here.

00:09:58.825 --> 00:09:59.639
There are two types of schools.

00:10:01.100 --> 00:10:06.200
There's the school of 'I want to become the best at what I do,

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:07.897
and I'm going to focus on my strengths'

00:10:08.481 --> 00:10:10.299
so I can become the go-to person.

00:10:11.121 --> 00:10:13.738
Who was at marchand de biens two Saturdays ago?

