00:11:27.519 --> 00:11:29.120
and you're going to lose money at some point

00:11:29.544 --> 00:11:30.700
and not become number 1.

00:11:30.779 --> 00:11:33.799
Because to be number 1, you have to really focus

00:11:34.244 --> 00:11:35.720
